'''''Virunga''''' ni filime documentaire yo mu Bwongereza yakinwe muri 2014 iyobowe na Orlando von Einsiedel<ref name=":0">Three separate films - Africa Is a Country <nowiki>https://africasacountry.com</nowiki> › 2015/04 › virunga-is-an-i...</ref> . Yibanze ku bikorwa byo kubungabunga abashinzwe parike muri pariki ya [[Pariki y’Ibirunga ya Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Virunga ya]] [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Kongo]] mu gihe havutse imyigaragambyo ikaze ya M23 mu mwaka wa 2012<ref name=":1">Virunga - Films for the Earth <nowiki>https://filmsfortheearth.org</nowiki> › Home › Films</ref>, kandi ikora iperereza ku bikorwa by’isosiyete ikora peteroli yo mu Bwongereza Soco International mu murage ndangamurage wa UNESCO<ref name=":1" />.  Soco International yarangije gushakisha peteroli muri Virunga muri Mata 2014<ref name=":0" />.  Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Tribeca ku ya 17 Mata 2014<ref>Virunga | 2014 Tribeca Festival <nowiki>https://tribecafilm.com</nowiki> › festival › archive › 53208a9dc...</ref>. Nyuma yo gutambuka kuri Netflix, yatorewe igihembo cya Akademiki ya Best Documentary Feature <ref>[Tribeca Review] Virunga - The Film Stage <nowiki>https://thefilmstage.com</nowiki> › tribeca-review-virunga</ref>.<ref>Virunga: Tribeca Review - The Hollywood Reporter <nowiki>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com</nowiki> › general-news › v...</ref>
