=== Ibihembo ===
''Virunga'' yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi harimo na Peabody Award .<ref>Film Support from Production to Impact - Bertha Foundation <nowiki>https://berthafoundation.org</nowiki> › Shorthand</ref> Feature documentaire Award ku DOXA documentaire Festival mu Vancouver, Canada; igihembo cy'umukinnyi mpuzamahanga wavutse muri Hot Docs i Toronto<ref>Trailer: Netflix Doc 'Virunga' Fights for World's Last Mountain ... <nowiki>https://www.indiewire.com</nowiki> › 2014/09 › trailer-netflix-d...</ref>; Igihembo cya Zahabu ya Rock mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime Ntoya<ref>Congo's famous mountain gorilla Ndakasi dies at 14 in ... <nowiki>https://www.theglobeandmail.com</nowiki> › world › article-con...</ref>; n'Ibikorwa no Guhinduka Hamwe (ACT Now) Igihembo cya Crested Butte Film Festival . Yatsindiye gongs ebyiri muri One World Media Awards muri BAFTA - Inyandiko nziza<ref>Bafta nomination for Virunga - Miikka Leskinen <nowiki>https://miikkaleskinen.com</nowiki> › bafta-nomination-for-viru...</ref>, . Iyi filime kandi yatorewe igihembo cyiza cya Documentaire nziza muri Tribeca Film Festival.  Filime yatorewe igihembo cya Akademiki kubera ibihembo bya Documentaire Nziza ya 87 ya Osama Awards <ref>Oscar Nominated 'Virunga' Instrumental in Protecting Africa's Oldest National Park - EcoWatch</ref>.

